The scripts assume a workspace folder with the following structure:

workspace : root folder
|
|-> executables : scripts folder with yalff executable
|
|-> reference : contains the reference fasta file and its indexed version
|
|-> results : folder containing the results
    |
    |-> smooth : folder containing the smoothed gzipped datasets
    |
    |-> pipeline : SNP calling results
|
|-> tools : folder containing the tools (bwa, rtg plot, etc.)
|
| -> working_datasets : folder with the original downloaded datsets (in gzip format).
|
|-> quartz_files : folder for quartz and leon files. Contains the dictionary for quartz and the uncompressed datasets in fastq format.